<div id="jd-header" class="guide-header" style="width: 693px; height: 53px">
  <span class="crumb">
    
      <a href="index.html">User Interface</a> >
    
  </span>
<h1 style="width: 709px">Declaring Layout——声明布局</h1>
</div>

  <div id="jd-content">


    <div class="jd-descr">
    <div id="qv-wrapper">
<div id="qv">
  <h2>Key classes——关键类</h2>
  <ol>
    <li><code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/View.html">View</a></code></li>
    <li><code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/ViewGroup.html">ViewGroup</a></code></li>
    <li><code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/ViewGroup.LayoutParams.html">ViewGroup.LayoutParams</a></code></li>
  </ol>
  <h2>In this document——这篇文档中</h2>
  <ol>
    <li><a href="#write">Write t<span class="style1">he XML</span></a>——编写XML文件</li>
    <li><a href="#load">Load the XML Resource</a>——加载XML资源文件</li>
    <li><a href="#attributes">Attributes</a>
      ——参数<ol>
        <li><a href="#id">ID</a></li>
        <li><a href="#layout-params">Layout Parameters</a>——布局参数</li>
      </ol>
    </li>
    <li><a href="#Position">Position</a>——显示位置</li>
    <li><a href="#SizePaddingMargin">Size, Padding and Margins</a>——尺寸，填充和边距</li>
    <li><a href="#example">Example Layout</a>——实例布局</li>
  </ol>

</div>
</div>

<p style="width: 716px">Your layout is the architecture for the user interface in an Activity.
It defines the layout structure and holds all the elements that appear to the user. 
You can declare your layout in two ways:<br>
您的布局是活动中用户界面的架构。他定义了布局结构而且承载了所有显示给用户的元素。您可以以下列两种方式声明您的布局：</p>
<ul>
<li style="width: 690px"><strong>Declare UI elements in XML</strong>. Android provides a straightforward XML 
vocabulary that corresponds to the View classes and subclasses, such as those for widgets and layouts.<br>
<strong>在XML文件中声明UI元素。</strong>Android提供了简单的 
与View类及子类对应的XML名称集，例如控件和布局的在XML中的名称。</li>
<li style="width: 688px"><strong>Instantiate layout elements at runtime</strong>. Your 
application can create View and ViewGroup objects (and manipulate their properties) programmatically. 
<br>
<strong>在运行时实例化布局元素。</strong>您的应用程序可以可编程地创建 View和 ViewGroup对象（并且控制他们的属性）。</li>
</ul>

<p style="width: 716px; height: 77px">The Android framework gives you the flexibility to use either or both of these methods for declaring and managing your application's UI. For example, you could declare your application's default layouts in XML, including the screen elements that will appear in them and their properties. You could then add code in your application that would modify the state of the screen objects, including those declared in XML, at run time. 
<br>
Android框架给您&nbsp;&nbsp; 使用任一个或两个均使用来进行应用程序UI的声明和管理的&nbsp;&nbsp; 
自由。举例来说，您可以在XML文件中定义您应用程序的默认布局，包括屏幕元素和他们的属性。然后您可以向您的应用程序中添加代码来 在运行时 
修改屏幕对象的状态，包括在XML中定义的。</p>

<div class="sidebox">
  <ul>
  <li>The <a href="../../../sdk/eclipse-adt.html">ADT
  Plugin for Eclipse</a> offers a layout preview of your XML &mdash; 
  with the XML file opened, select the <strong>Layout</strong> tab.<br>
	<a href="../../../sdk/eclipse-adt.html">ADT
  Plugin for Eclipse</a>提供XML布局预览功能——即打开XML文件，选择<strong>Layout</strong> 标签。</li>
  <li>You should also try the 
  <a href="../../../guide/developing/tools/hierarchy-viewer.html">Hierarchy Viewer</a> tool, 
  for debugging layouts &mdash; it reveals layout property values, 
  draws wireframes with padding/margin indicators, and full rendered views while 
  you debug on the emulator or device.<br>
	您也应该试一下<a href="../../../guide/developing/tools/hierarchy-viewer.html">Hierarchy Viewer</a>工具，进行布局调试——您在模拟器或设备上进行调试时，他显示布局的属性值，画出网格，显示边距和填充，和已经完全安排好的可视窗。</li>
  <li>The <a href="../../../guide/developing/tools/layoutopt.html">layoutopt</a> tool lets
  you quickly analyze your layouts and hierarchies for inefficiencies or other problems.<br>
	<a href="../../../guide/developing/tools/layoutopt.html">layoutopt</a>工具让您可以快速的分析布局和层级的不足或其它问题。</li>
</div>

<p style="width: 766px">The advantage to declaring your UI in XML is that it enables you to better separate the presentation of your application from the code that controls its behavior. Your UI descriptions are external to your application code, which means that you can modify or adapt it without having to modify your source code and recompile. For example, you can create XML layouts for different screen orientations, different device screen sizes, and different languages. Additionally, declaring the layout in XML makes it easier to visualize the structure of your UI, so it's easier to debug problems. As such, this document focuses on teaching you how to declare your layout in XML. If you're
interested in instantiating View objects at runtime, refer to the <code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/ViewGroup.html">ViewGroup</a></code> and 
<code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/View.html">View</a></code> class references.<br>
在XML中声明您的UI的好处是他可以使您更好的将应用程序的显示部分和控制其行为的代码部分分开。您的UI描述在您应用程序代码的外部，这就意味着如果您改动UI描述，您不用更改您的代码部分，也不用对其重新编译。例如，您可以为不同的屏幕方向、不同屏幕尺寸的设备、不同的语言创建XML布局配置。而且，在XML中声明布局可以使您的UI的结构更明显，这样一来就更好进行调试了。因此，这篇文档着重讲了如何使用XMl文件进行布局声明。如果您对&nbsp; 
在运行时进行View的实例化来达到布局目的，请转到 <code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/ViewGroup.html">ViewGroup</a></code>和<code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/View.html">View</a></code> 
类的参考。</p>

<p style="width: 763px">In general, the XML vocabulary for declaring UI elements closely follows the structure and naming of the classes and methods, where element names correspond to class names and attribute names correspond to methods. In fact, the correspondence is often so direct that you can guess what XML attribute corresponds to a class method, or guess what class corresponds to a given xml element. However, note that not all vocabulary is identical. In some cases, there are slight naming differences. For
example, the EditText element has a <code>text</code> attribute that corresponds to
<code>EditText.setText()</code>. <br>
一般来说，用于声明UI元素的 XML名称集 
与类和方法的名称很相似，元素名称和类名相对应、属性名称和方法相对应。实际上，名称相符到您可以直接猜出和类方法名相对应的XML元素属性，或者猜出和给定XML元素相对应的类名。但是，注意不是每个元素都能在类或方法中找到对应。有些时候，也是稍有不同。例如，EditText元素有一个<code>text</code>属性，和<code>EditText.setText()</code>对应。</p>

<p class="note"><strong>Tip:</strong> Learn more about different layout types in <a href="../../../guide/topics/ui/layout-objects.html">Common
Layout Objects</a>. There are also a collection of tutorials on building various layouts in the
<a href="../../../guide/tutorials/views/index.html">Hello Views</a> tutorial guide.<br>
<strong>小贴士：</strong>学习更多不同类型的布局，参考<a href="../../../guide/topics/ui/layout-objects.html">Common
Layout Objects</a>。<a href="../../../guide/tutorials/views/index.html">Hello Views</a> 
指南中还有一系列关于建立不同类型布局的指南。</p>

<h2 id="write">Write the XML——编写XML</h2>

<div class="sidebox"><p>For your convenience, the API reference documentation for UI related classes lists the available XML attributes that correspond to the class methods, including inherited attributes.<br>
	为方便起见，API参考文档中与UI有关的类列举了可用的与类方法相对应的XML属性，包括集成的属性。</p>
<p>To learn more about the available XML elements and attributes, as well as the format of the XML file, see <a
href="../../../guide/topics/resources/available-resources.html#layoutresources">Layout Resources</a>.<br>
更多有关可用的XML元素和属性，还有XML文件格式，参看<a
href="../../../guide/topics/resources/available-resources.html#layoutresources">Layout Resources</a>。</p>
 </div>

<p>Using Android's XML vocabulary, you can quickly design UI layouts and the screen elements they contain, in the same way you create web pages in HTML &mdash; with a series of nested elements. 
<br>
使用Android的XML名称集，您可以快速的设计UI布局和他们包含的屏幕元素，就像您在使用HTML语言——使用一系列嵌套的元素创建一个网页一样。</p>

<p>Each layout file must contain exactly one root element, which must be a View or ViewGroup object. Once you've defined the root element, you can add additional layout objects or widgets as child elements to gradually build a View hierarchy that defines your layout. For example, here's an XML layout that uses a vertical <code><a href="../../../reference/android/widget/LinearLayout.html">LinearLayout</a></code>
to hold a <code><a href="../../../reference/android/widget/TextView.html">TextView</a></code> and a <code><a href="../../../reference/android/widget/Button.html">Button</a></code>:<br>
每一个布局文件必须只包含一个根元素，根元素必须是一个View或 ViewGroup 
对象。您定义了根元素之后，就可以向其中添加其他的布局对象或者控件作为子元素，最终建造一个View层级，这个层级就是您定义的布局。例如，下面是一个XML布局，使用了垂直<code><a href="../../../reference/android/widget/LinearLayout.html">LinearLayout</a>（线型布局）</code>组织一个<code><a href="../../../reference/android/widget/TextView.html">TextView</a></code>和一个<code><a href="../../../reference/android/widget/Button.html">Button</a></code>：</p>
<pre>
&lt;?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
&lt;LinearLayout xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
              android:layout_width="fill_parent" 
              android:layout_height="fill_parent" 
              android:orientation="vertical" >
    &lt;TextView android:id="@+id/text"
              android:layout_width="wrap_content"
              android:layout_height="wrap_content"
              android:text="Hello, I am a TextView" />
    &lt;Button android:id="@+id/button"
            android:layout_width="wrap_content"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:text="Hello, I am a Button" />
&lt;/LinearLayout>
</pre>

<p>After you've declared your layout in XML, save the file with the <code>.xml</code> extension, 
in your Android project's <code>res/layout/</code> directory, so it will properly compile. 
<br>
您在XML中完成布局的声明后，使用<code>.xml</code> 扩展名保存这个文件，保存在Android项目的<code>res/layout/</code> 
directory文件夹下，这样就可以顺利编译了。</p>

<p>We'll discuss each of the attributes shown here a little later.<br>
后面我们会详细讨论上面例子中出现的元素的属性。</p>

<h2 id="load">Load the XML Resource——加载XML资源</h2>

<p>When you compile your application, each XML layout file is compiled into a
<code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/View.html">View</a></code> resource. You should load the layout resource from your application code, in your 
<code><a href="../../../reference/android/app/Activity.html#onCreate(android.os.Bundle)">Activity.onCreate()</a></code> callback implementation.
Do so by calling <code><code><a href="../../../reference/android/app/Activity.html#setContentView(int)">setContentView()</a></code></code>, 
passing it the reference to your layout resource in the form of: 
<code>R.layout.<em>layout_file_name</em></code>  
For example, if your XML layout is saved as <code>main_layout.xml</code>, you would load it
for your Activity like so:<br>
在您编译您的应用程序时，每一个XML布局文件被便以为一个<code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/View.html">View</a></code>资源。您应该从您的应用程序中加载布局资源，就是从您的<code><a href="../../../reference/android/app/Activity.html#onCreate(android.os.Bundle)">Activity.onCreate()</a></code>回调的实现中。调用<code><a href="../../../reference/android/app/Activity.html#setContentView(int)">setContentView()</a></code>完成此事，并以这个形式将布局资源的引用传进去：<code>R.layout.<em>layout_file_name </em></code>  
。例如如果您的XML布局保存为<code>main_layout.xml</code>，您就可以像这样为您的活动加载他：</p>
<pre>
public void onCreate(Bundle savedInstanceState) {
    super.onCreate(savedInstanceState);
    setContentView.(R.layout.main_layout);
}
</pre>

<p>The <code>onCreate()</code> callback method in your Activity is called by the Android framework when
your Activity is launched (see the discussion on Lifecycles, in the 
<a href="../../../guide/topics/fundamentals.html#lcycles">Application Fundamantals</a>, for more on this).<br>
活动中的<code>onCreate()</code>回调方法在您的活动被加载时由Android系统调用（参见在生命周期中讨论的内容，在<a href="../../../guide/topics/fundamentals.html#lcycles">Application Fundamantals</a>了解更多）</p>


<h2 id="attributes">Attributes——属性</h2>

<p>Every View and ViewGroup object supports their own variety of XML attributes.
Some attributes are specific to a View object (for example, TextView supports the <code>textSize</code>
attribute), but these attributes are also inherited by any View objects that may extend this class.
Some are common to all View objects, because they are inherited from the root View class (like 
the <code>id</code> attribute). And, other attributes are considered "layout parameters," which are 
attributes that describe certain layout orientations of the View object, as defined by that object's
parent ViewGroup object.<br>
每个View和ViewGroup对象都支持他自己的一组XML属性。有些属性是某个View对象特有的（例如，TextView支持<code>textSize</code>属性），但是，这些属性也会被从这个类继承的的View对象拥有。有些对所有View对象都是通用的（像<code>id</code> 
属性），因为他们是从同一个根View继承来的。还有，其他的属性被视为“布局参数”，就是描述View对象额特殊布局方向的参数，是由对象的父ViewGroup对象定义的。</p>

<h3 id="id">ID</h3>

<p>Any View object may have an integer ID associated with it, to uniquely identify the View within the tree.
When the application is compiled, this ID is referenced as an integer, but the ID is typically 
assigned in the layout XML file as a string, in the <code>id</code> attribute.
This is an XML attribute common to all View objects
(defined by the <code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/View.html">View</a></code> class) and you will use it very often. 
The syntax for an ID, inside an XML tag is:<br>
每个View对象都会被分配一个整数的ID，以在层级树中有唯一的识别方式。应用程序在编译的时候，ID用一个整数引用，但是ID在XML布局文件中是以字符串的形式出现的，在<code>id</code>属性中。这是一个所有View对象（由<code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/View.html">View</a></code>类定义）通用的XML属性，您会经常使用他。在XML标签中，定义ID的语法是：</p>
<pre>android:id="&#64;+id/my_button"</pre>

<p>The  at-symbol (&#64;) at the beginning of the string indicates that the XML parser should parse and expand the rest
of the ID string and identify it as an ID resource. The plus-symbol (+) means that this is a new resource name that must
be created and added to our resources (in the <code>R.java</code> file). There are a number of other ID resources that
are offered by the Android framework. When referencing an Android resource ID, you do not need the plus-symbol,
but must add the <code>android</code> package namespace, like so:<br>
字符串开头的at符号（@）表明XML解析器应解析并展开字符串后边的部分，然后识别为ID资源。加号（+）的意思是这是一个新的资源名称，需要新建然后添加到已有资源（在<code>R.java</code>文件中）文件中。Android架构还提供了其他大量的ID资源。当引用一个Android资源ID时，您不需要加上加号，但是必须像下边示例一样添加 <code>android</code> 
包的名称空间：</p>
<pre>android:id="&#64;android:id/empty"</pre>
<p>With the <code>android</code> package namespace in place, we're now referencing an ID from the <code>android.R</code>
resources class, rather than the local resources class.<br>
添加<code>android</code> 包名称空间后，您就可以引用 <code>android.R</code>资源类中ID，而不是本地资源类。</p>

<p>In order to create views and reference them from the application, a common pattern is to:<br>
为了创建一个可视窗，然后从应用程序中引用，通常是这样做：</p>
<ol>
  <li>Define a view/widget in the layout file and assign it a unique ID:
<br>
	在布局文件中定义一个可视窗/控件，然后为其分配一个唯一的ID：
<pre>
&lt;Button android:id="&#64;+id/my_button"
        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
        android:text="&#64;string/my_button_text"/>
</pre>
  </li>
  <li>Then create an instance of the view object and capture it from the layout 
(typically in the <code><code><a href="../../../reference/android/app/Activity.html#onCreate(android.os.Bundle)">onCreate()</a></code></code> method):
	<br>
	然后创建一个可视窗对象的实例，然后从布局中获取他（一般在 <code><a href="../../../reference/android/app/Activity.html#onCreate(android.os.Bundle)">onCreate()</a></code>方法中完成）：<pre>
Button myButton = (Button) findViewById(R.id.my_button);
</pre>
  </li>
</ol>
<p>Defining IDs for view objects is important when creating a <code><a href="../../../reference/android/widget/RelativeLayout.html">RelativeLayout</a></code>.
In a relative layout, sibling views can define their layout relative to another sibling view, 
which is referenced by the unique ID.<br>
为可视窗对象定义ID是创建一个<code><a href="../../../reference/android/widget/RelativeLayout.html">RelativeLayout</a></code>的重要步骤。在一个相对布局中，位置相关的一组可视窗的布局可以由其中一个确定，这个确定位置的可视窗由唯一的ID引用。</p>
<p>An ID need not be unique throughout the entire tree, but it should be
unique within the part of the tree you are searching (which may often be the entire tree, so it's best 
to be completely unique when possible).<br>
ID在整个树中不必唯一，但是在顺着树进行查找的时候，在查找的线路中必须是唯一的（查找过程经常涉及整个树，所以如果可以请尽量使用绝对唯一的ID）。</p>


<h3 id="layout-params">Layout Parameters——布局参数</h3>

<p>XML layout attributes named <code>layout_<em>something</em></code> define 
layout parameters for the View that are appropriate for the ViewGroup in which it resides.<br>
叫做的<code>layout_<em>something</em></code>&nbsp;&nbsp; 
XML布局属性定义了他所在的ViewGroup中的View布的局参数。</p>

<p>Every ViewGroup class implements a nested class that extends <code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/ViewGroup.LayoutParams.html">ViewGroup.LayoutParams</a></code>. This subclass
contains property types that define the size and position for each child view, as
appropriate for the view group. As you can see in the figure below, the parent
view group defines layout parameters for each child view (including the child view group).<br>
每个ViewGroup类实现了一组嵌套的由<code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/ViewGroup.LayoutParams.html">ViewGroup.LayoutParams</a></code>继承来的类。这个子类包含了定义了每个子可视窗大小和位置的性质类型，并且是适合这个可视窗组的。就像您在下边图示中看到的，父可视窗组定义了每个子可视窗的布局参数（包括子可视窗组）。</p>

<img src="../../../images/layoutparams.png" alt="" height="300" align="center"/>

	<br>
	<img alt="布局参数图示" src="../../../images/layoutparamsTr.png" width="514" height="300"><p>Note that every LayoutParams subclass has its own syntax for setting
values. Each child element must define LayoutParams that are appropriate for its parent, 
though it may also define different LayoutParams for its own children. <br>
	注意每个LayoutParams子类都有他自己的设定参数的语法。每个子元素必须定义适合他所在父的LayoutParams，虽然他也要定义和父不同的子的LayoutParams。</p>

<p>All view groups include a width and height (<code>layout_width</code> and <code>layout_height</code>), 
and each view is required to define them. 
Many LayoutParams also include optional margins and
borders. You can specify width and height with exact measurements, though you probably won't want
to do this often. More often, you will tell your view to size itself either to
the dimensions required by its content, or to become as big as its parent view group
will allow (with the <var>wrap_content</var> and <var>fill_parent</var> values, respectively).
The accepted measurement types are defined in the 
<a href="../../../guide/topics/resources/available-resources.html#dimension">
Available Resources</a> document.<br>
所有的可视窗组包含宽和高（<code>layout_width</code> 和 <code>layout_height</code>），每一个可视窗都必须定义他们。许多LayoutParams还有可选的边距和边框。您可以为宽和高指定精确地数值，但是您一般不会这样做。更常见的情况是，您会让您的可视窗自己根据&nbsp;&nbsp; 
其中内容要求&nbsp;&nbsp; 或&nbsp; 尽可能填充满父可视窗&nbsp;&nbsp; （分别是使用使用<var>wrap_content</var> 
和<var>fill_parent</var>值）为自己设定大小。可用的测量大小的方式在 
<a href="../../../guide/topics/resources/available-resources.html#dimension">
Available Resources</a> 文档中有定义。</p>


<h2 id="Position">Layout Position——布局位置</h2>
   <p>
   The geometry of a view is that of a rectangle. A view has a location,
   expressed as a pair of <em>left</em> and <em>top</em> coordinates, and
   two dimensions, expressed as a width and a height. The unit for location
   and dimensions is the pixel.
   <br>
	可视窗的几何形状是矩形。可视窗有其位置，用一组&nbsp;&nbsp; 左上角相对坐标和可视窗宽高&nbsp;&nbsp; 
	值表示。相对坐标和宽高的单位是像素。</p>
  
   <p>
   It is possible to retrieve the location of a view by invoking the methods
   <code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/View.html#getLeft()">getLeft()</a></code> and <code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/View.html#getTop()">getTop()</a></code>. The former returns the left, or X,
   coordinate of the rectangle representing the view. The latter returns the
   top, or Y, coordinate of the rectangle representing the view. These methods
   both return the location of the view relative to its parent. For instance,
   when getLeft() returns 20, that means the view is located 20 pixels to the
   right of the left edge of its direct parent.
   <br>
	您可以通过调用
   <code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/View.html#getLeft()">getLeft()</a></code> 
	和<code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/View.html#getTop()">getTop()</a></code>方法获取可视窗位置。前者返回代表可视窗的矩形 
	距左边线距离，或者说X坐标。后者返回代表可视窗的矩形 
	距上边线距离，或者说Y坐标。这两个方法返回的距离是相对父可视窗的。例如，如果getLeft()函数返回20，意思就是可视窗距他直接的父的左边线的距离为20个像素。</p>
  
   <p>
   In addition, several convenience methods are offered to avoid unnecessary
   computations, namely <code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/View.html#getRight()">getRight()</a></code> and <code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/View.html#getBottom()">getBottom()</a></code>.
   These methods return the coordinates of the right and bottom edges of the
   rectangle representing the view. For instance, calling <code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/View.html#getRight()">getRight()</a></code>
   is similar to the following computation: <code>getLeft() + getWidth()</code>.
   <br>
	还有，为避免不必要的计算，我们还提供了一些方便的方法，<code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/View.html#getRight()">getRight()</a></code>和<code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/View.html#getBottom()">getBottom()</a></code>。这两个方法返回的是代表可视窗的矩形的右下角的相对坐标。比如，调用<code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/View.html#getRight()">getRight()</a></code>就同下面的计算是相同的： <code>getLeft() + getWidth()</code>。</p>
   

<h2 id="SizePaddingMargins">Size, Padding and Margins——尺寸，填充和边距</h2>
   <p>
   The size of a view is expressed with a width and a height. A view actually
   possess two pairs of width and height values.
   <br>
	可视窗的尺寸是由宽和高表示的。一个可视窗实际上含有两对宽高值。</p>
  
   <p>
   The first pair is known as <em>measured width</em> and
   <em>measured height</em>. These dimensions define how big a view wants to be
   within its parent. The
   measured dimensions can be obtained by calling <code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/View.html#getMeasuredWidth()">getMeasuredWidth()</a></code>
   and <code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/View.html#getMeasuredHeight()">getMeasuredHeight()</a></code>.
   <br>
	一对是&nbsp;&nbsp; 测量的宽 和 测量的高 。这对值表示了您希望这个可视窗在其父中的大小。获取一个可视窗的&nbsp; 测量的宽 和 
	测量的高&nbsp; 值可调用<code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/View.html#getMeasuredWidth()">getMeasuredWidth()</a></code>和<code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/View.html#getMeasuredHeight()">getMeasuredHeight()</a></code>。</p>
  
   <p>
   The second pair is simply known as <em>width</em> and <em>height</em>, or
   sometimes <em>drawing width</em> and <em>drawing height</em>. These
   dimensions define the actual size of the view on screen, at drawing time and
   after layout. These values may, but do not have to, be different from the
   measured width and height. The width and height can be obtained by calling
   <code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/View.html#getWidth()">getWidth()</a></code> and <code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/View.html#getHeight()">getHeight()</a></code>. 
   <br>
	第二对就是平常所说的 宽 和 高，或者叫做 绘图宽 和 绘图高 。这对值定义了可视窗在屏幕上的实际尺寸，是在布局后的绘制时期确定的。这对值可能会，但不是一定会&nbsp; 
	和测量的宽高 不同。获取一个可视窗的&nbsp; 绘图宽 和 绘图高&nbsp; 值可调用<code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/View.html#getWidth()">getWidth()</a></code>和<code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/View.html#getHeight()">getHeight()</a></code>。</p>
  
   <p>
   To measure its dimensions, a view takes into account its padding. The padding
   is expressed in pixels for the left, top, right and bottom parts of the view.
   Padding can be used to offset the content of the view by a specific amount of
   pixels. For instance, a left padding of 2 will push the view's content by
   2 pixels to the right of the left edge. Padding can be set using the
   <code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/View.html#setPadding(int, int, int, int)">setPadding(int, int, int, int)</a></code> method and queried by calling
   <code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/View.html#getPaddingLeft()">getPaddingLeft()</a></code>, <code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/View.html#getPaddingTop()">getPaddingTop()</a></code>,
   <code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/View.html#getPaddingRight()">getPaddingRight()</a></code> and <code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/View.html#getPaddingBottom()">getPaddingBottom()</a></code>.  
   <br>
	决定他的宽和高，可视窗会考虑其填充物的大小。填充物用其可视窗的左上和右下角部分的坐标表示。填充物可以以特定数量的像素填充可视窗中内容四周的地方。例如，两个像素的左填充会将可视窗的内容向右推两个像素。填充可由方法<code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/View.html#setPadding(int, int, int, int)">setPadding(int, int, int, int)</a></code>设定，调用
   <code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/View.html#getPaddingLeft()">getPaddingLeft()</a></code>, <code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/View.html#getPaddingTop()">getPaddingTop()</a></code>,
   <code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/View.html#getPaddingRight()">getPaddingRight()</a></code> 
	和 <code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/View.html#getPaddingBottom()">getPaddingBottom()</a></code>获取。</p>
  
   <p>
   Even though a view can define a padding, it does not provide any support for
   margins. However, view groups provide such a support. Refer to
   <code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/ViewGroup.html">ViewGroup</a></code> and
   <code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/ViewGroup.MarginLayoutParams.html">ViewGroup.MarginLayoutParams</a></code> for further information.
   <br>
	虽然可视窗可以定义填充物，但是他不支持边距。但是可视窗组有这样的功能。参见<code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/ViewGroup.html">ViewGroup</a></code>和<code><a href="../../../reference/android/view/ViewGroup.MarginLayoutParams.html">ViewGroup.MarginLayoutParams</a></code>获取更多信息。</p>

<p>For more information about dimensions, see <a href="../../../guide/topics/resources/available-resources.html#dimension">Dimension Values</a>.<br>
更多有关这两种维度的信息，参见<a href="../../../guide/topics/resources/available-resources.html#dimension">Dimension Values</a>。</p>
   




